multi_tenant_systems.name: StillMe Enterprise Multi-Tenant Platform
multi_tenant_systems.description: Enterprise-grade multi-tenant platform for StillMe AI
multi_tenant_systems.isolation_strategy: Hybrid isolation with database-level for enterprise, schema-level for SMB, row-level for others
multi_tenant_systems.scaling_strategy: Auto-scaling based on resource utilization with tenant-specific thresholds
multi_tenant_systems.security_framework: Multi-layer security with tenant-specific access controls and encryption
multi_tenant_systems.compliance_framework: Automated compliance monitoring with tenant-specific requirements
multi_tenant_systems.monitoring_system: Real-time monitoring with tenant-specific dashboards and alerting
multi_tenant_systems.backup_strategy: Automated backup with tenant-specific retention policies and geographic distribution

recommendations.recommendation: Implement hybrid isolation strategy with database-level for enterprise tenants
recommendations.rationale: Database-level isolation provides maximum security for enterprise customers while maintaining cost efficiency

recommendations.recommendation: Implement intelligent auto-scaling with tenant-specific thresholds
recommendations.rationale: Tenant-specific thresholds ensure optimal resource utilization while maintaining SLA requirements

recommendations.recommendation: Implement multi-layer security with tenant-specific access controls
recommendations.rationale: Multi-layer security ensures enterprise-grade protection while maintaining flexibility

recommendations.recommendation: Automate compliance monitoring with tenant-specific requirements
recommendations.rationale: Automated compliance reduces manual overhead and ensures consistent adherence to regulations
